cdata.name: SalPay
cdata.desc:
Salariumis an online platform situatedin the Philippines. Itworks as an intermediary between Companies and Employees by providing users with features to monitor thework schedules and payroll requirements.

SalPayis an Ethereum-based token developed by Salariumplatform.It aims to be a business tool to help individuals and organizationsto send money in south-eastAsia with fewer costs and hassles. SAL can be used by Salariumusers to send payments to either freelancer or directly hired employees. SalPay's3.0will be an ERC20-based algorithm wallet to hold SalPay and other Ethereum-based tokens.
